{"tid":354521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"買💍想買得值嘅巴打可以入入黎","createTime":"2017-08-10T13:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T14:00:39.000Z","uid":135162,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce1f9b630d706825a9de3b402fff81c644dd7a9","tid":354521,"uid":135162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:55:56.000Z","msg":"其實買鑽戒邊有巴打會覺得值架? 不過真是要買嘅，我諗呢間都真係幾抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾個禮拜前，仲煩緊邊度有好款嘅戒指環做求婚戒指，朋友就介紹左間近炮台山嘅珠寶舖頭睇。<br />\n<br />\n老闆娘同d員工態度都好好，見我唔係太識，解釋得好清楚鑽石點分grade，唔似得某某舖頭一入去就唔理你，而我睇唔岩款果陣又會比好多建議，真係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鑽石有GIA認證，唔係淘返黎(知道cert都可以淘)，佢地有laser機對粒石個number，比你上網check。<br />\n<br />\n店裡面除左鑽戒，仲有結婚對戒，或者其他鑽石，巴打如果岩嘅可以考慮去睇睇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bluefine.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bluefine.hk&d=ZmXSrbDKmsQzFN1FCt4cqsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5be7052a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bluefine.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/213310_f9fb5735f442a483b57b1aef13e5bafb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F213310_f9fb5735f442a483b57b1aef13e5bafb.jpg&h=10c519a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/213311_277d9d3e4f4a436e0fcb7a6cc10919a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F213311_277d9d3e4f4a436e0fcb7a6cc10919a1.jpg&h=9b77efdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/213312_6c698fb5f2b2e155db92db6a55fc225d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F213312_6c698fb5f2b2e155db92db6a55fc225d.jpg&h=f2f8fb92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/213313_175e5c0990bd7324ecdad30c6c354d59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F213313_175e5c0990bd7324ecdad30c6c354d59.jpg&h=9e80d0bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/213315_aaf896f7e5b045b4f81f37680d87cd6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F213315_aaf896f7e5b045b4f81f37680d87cd6c.jpg&h=2f62a4ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ef646119f4be99808c13b4d58f3daef7efcda06","tid":354521,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:57:05.000Z","msg":"想用連登賣廣告？"},{"pid":"ab37d0a68ce89bd315101f57c392487c40ef7595","tid":354521,"uid":21980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T14:00:39.000Z","msg":"十成九打手"}]}